# SEO Writer Agent - Cursor Rules

## Project Identity
- **Name:** SEO Content Pipeline
- **Philosophy:** Data-driven, Anti-AI vibe, Modular Sub-agents.

## Navigation & Structure
- **Agents:** Definitions are in `.antigravity/agents/`. Refer to them when performing specific tasks (e.g., Use `seo-collector.md` when doing SERP research).
- **Rules:** Pipeline logic is in `CLAUDE.md`.
- **Knowledge Base:** Always check `resources/` before assuming company facts.

## Commands (Simulation)
When the user types a slash command, follow the logic defined in `CLAUDE.md`:
- `/write`: Follow the pipeline (SEO Collector -> Main Agent -> Brand Guardian -> Quality Guardian).
- `/setup`: Invoke `research-agent.md` logic.
- `/approve`: Update the YAML `Status` field in the active file.

## Token Optimization
- **Do not read entire directories.** Use `list_dir` to see structure first.
- **Do not read full content files** if you only need the metadata. Read the first 20 lines.
- **Summarize research** before drafting to keep context clean.

## Writing Style
- Vietnamese by default (unless specified).
- Professional, actionable, evidence-based.
- Strictly follow `templates/seo-strategy/resources/content-strategy/anti-ai-rules.md`.
